data.description:
Beautiful single family home for sale by owner. 
3 Bedrooms, 2. 5 bathrooms,
Completed upgraded!
All appliances included. Fully upgraded top of the line products.
Just finished by Fisher homes in April 2023
Clean back yard and brand new concreted stamped patio.
Patio furniture included and also some furniture.
2 cars garage.
Kitchen, closets, laundry room and garage fully upgraded. Must see!
Eager to sell, open to reasonable offers.
Home still under warranty.
data.whatILove:
New home, large back yard with stamp
Concrete patio, additional fire pit area.
Full of upgrades around the house.
